{%- comment -%}
  SOP: Great Offer Bundle section
  =================================

  Purpose
  -------
  This section shows tiered bundle cards, opens a scent-selection modal, lets the
  customer choose the exact quantity of bottles included in the selected tier,
  and adds the selected variants to cart in one request.

  Files required when moving this feature to another Shopify theme
  ----------------------------------------------------------------
  1. Copy this file to:
     sections/great-offer.liquid
  2. Copy the JavaScript file to:
     assets/great-offer.js
  3. Keep this script include near the bottom of this section:
     <script src="{{ 'great-offer.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
  4. Add the section from the Shopify theme editor, or reference it from a JSON
     template with:
     "type": "great-offer"

  Product and variant setup requirements
  --------------------------------------
  - Each offer card uses a "Scent products" product list.
  - Every selected product must have a variant option value that matches the
    block setting "Size option value". Example: if the block says "50ml", the
    product variant option must also be "50ml".
  - The first product in the product list is used to display the card price for
    that size.
  - The modal will only show products that have a matching size variant.
  - Product images or variant images are used as scent thumbnails.

  Section/block setup in the theme editor
  ---------------------------------------
  - Section settings control the eyebrow, title, and subtitle.
  - "Tier Card" blocks are standard offer cards.
  - "Best Value Tier" is the highlighted offer card and is limited to one block.
  - For each block, set:
    products, size_label, size_option_value, qty_included, deal_tag_text,
    per_ml_label, per_ml_value, and button text.
  - The "qty_included" number is the exact quantity customers must choose before
    the Add to cart button becomes active.

  Theme compatibility notes
  -------------------------
  - This section uses Shopify's /cart/add.js endpoint through
    window.Shopify.routes.cart_add_url when available.
  - After adding items, the script dispatches the Horizon cart update event:
    cart:update
  - Themes that do not listen for cart:update will still add products to cart,
    but the cart drawer/page may not refresh automatically. In that case, update
    dispatchCartAddEvent() in assets/great-offer.js to match the target theme's
    cart refresh event, or redirect to /cart after a successful add.
  - The script looks for cart-items-component[data-section-id] to request cart
    sections for refresh. If the target theme uses different cart section
    markup, adjust the sectionIds logic in assets/great-offer.js.

  QA checklist after installing in another theme
  ---------------------------------------------
  - Add the section to a product/template page.
  - Select products for every tier card.
  - Confirm each tier's Size option value exactly matches real variant options.
  - Click each Choose button and confirm the modal opens with the right scents.
  - Confirm unavailable variants cannot be selected.
  - Select fewer than qty_included and confirm Add to cart stays disabled.
  - Select exactly qty_included and confirm the chosen variants add to cart.
  - Confirm the cart drawer/page refreshes correctly in the target theme.
  - Test on desktop and mobile widths.

  v1.0 by Monsur Riaz, 15 June 2026, for BCB Perfumes
  Screenshot: https://prnt.sc/eoiGXu88J1dn
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="great-offer-section">
  <div class="go-inner">
    <div class="go-header">
      <div class="go-eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow_text }}</div>
      <h2 class="go-title">{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
      <p class="go-subtitle">{{ section.settings.subtitle }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="go-cards">
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- assign block_products = block.settings.products -%}
        {%- assign size_option_value = block.settings.size_option_value -%}
        {%- assign qty = block.settings.qty_included -%}
        {%- assign is_featured = false -%}
        {%- if block.type == 'featured_offer_card' -%}
          {%- assign is_featured = true -%}
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- assign price_product = block_products | first -%}

        {%- if price_product -%}
          {%- comment -%} Find the variant matching this size {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- assign size_variant = nil -%}
          {%- for variant in price_product.variants -%}
            {%- if variant.option1 == size_option_value or variant.option2 == size_option_value or variant.option3 == size_option_value -%}
              {%- assign size_variant = variant -%}
              {%- break -%}
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}

          {%- if size_variant -%}
            {%- comment -%} Build scents array: block products × their size variant {%- endcomment -%}
            {%- assign scents_json_parts = '' -%}
            {%- for prod in block_products -%}
              {%- for var in prod.variants -%}
                {%- if var.option1 == size_option_value
                     or var.option2 == size_option_value
                     or var.option3 == size_option_value -%}
                  {%- unless scents_json_parts == '' -%}
                    {%- assign scents_json_parts = scents_json_parts | append: ',' -%}
                  {%- endunless -%}
                  {%- capture scent_obj -%}
                    {"id":{{ var.id }},"title":{{ prod.title | json }},"available":{{ var.available }},"image":"{{ var.featured_image | default: prod.featured_image | image_url: width: 100 }}"}
                  {%- endcapture -%}
                  {%- assign scents_json_parts = scents_json_parts | append: scent_obj -%}
                  {%- break -%}
                {%- endif -%}
              {%- endfor -%}
            {%- endfor -%}

            {%- assign scents_json = '[' | append: scents_json_parts | append: ']' -%}

            <div
              class="go-card{% if is_featured %} go-card--best{% endif %}"
              data-scents='{{ scents_json }}'
              data-qty="{{ qty }}"
              data-size-label="{{ block.settings.size_label }}"
              data-block-id="{{ block.id }}"
              {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
            >
              {%- if is_featured -%}
                <div class="go-best-label">
                  <span class="go-best-text-desktop">{{ block.settings.best_value_text }}</span>
                  <span class="go-best-text-mobile">{{ block.settings.best_value_text_mobile }}</span>
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

              <div class="go-size-badge">{{ block.settings.size_label }}</div>
              <div class="go-price">{{ size_variant.price | money }}</div>
              <div class="go-deal-tag{% if is_featured %} go-deal-tag--big{% endif %}">
                {{ block.settings.deal_tag_text }}
              </div>

              <div class="go-divider"></div>

              <div class="go-stat-row">
                <span>Bottles included</span>
                <span>× {{ qty }}</span>
              </div>

              <div class="go-ppm-row">
                <span class="go-ppm-label">{{ block.settings.per_ml_label }}</span>
                <span class="go-ppm-value{% if is_featured %} go-ppm-value--best{% endif %}">
                  {{ block.settings.per_ml_value }}
                </span>
              </div>

              {%- if is_featured and block.settings.saving_text != blank -%}
                <div class="go-saving">{{ block.settings.saving_text }}</div>
              {%- endif -%}

              <button
                class="go-btn{% if is_featured %} go-btn--best{% endif %}"
                type="button"
                data-action="go-start-flow"
              >
                <span class="go-btn-text">{{ block.settings.btn_text }}</span>
                <span class="go-btn-mobile-text">{{ block.settings.btn_text_mobile }}</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="go-modal" id="go-modal">
      <div class="go-modal-box">
        <button class="go-modal-close" type="button" id="go-modal-close">✕</button>
        <h3 id="go-modal-title">Choose your bottles</h3>
        <p id="go-modal-subtitle" class="go-modal-sub"></p>

        <!-- Progress Bar -->
        <div class="go-progress-wrap">
          <div class="go-progress-label">
            <span>Bottles chosen</span>
            <span><strong id="go-progress-n">0</strong> / <strong id="go-progress-total">2</strong></span>
          </div>
          <div class="go-progress-bar-bg">
            <div class="go-progress-bar-fill" id="go-progress-fill"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="go-scent-grid" id="go-scent-grid"></div>
        <div class="go-modal-footer">
          <span id="go-selection-count" class="go-sel-count">0 of 2 selected</span>
          <button class="go-confirm-btn" id="go-confirm-btn" type="button" disabled>
            Add to cart
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .great-offer-section * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .great-offer-section {
    --go-gold: #c9a84c;
    --go-gold-light: #e8d499;
    --go-dark: #1a1a1a;
    --go-cream: #faf7f2;
    --go-radius: 18px;
    background: var(--go-cream);
    padding: 70px 24px 80px;
  }

  .go-inner {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .go-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .go-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--go-gold);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .go-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--go-dark);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .go-subtitle {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #888;
    max-width: 440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .go-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .go-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--go-radius);
    border: 2px solid #e8e0d5;
    padding: 34px 26px 30px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1),
      box-shadow 0.25s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .go-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .go-card--best {
    background: var(--go-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--go-gold);
    color: #fff;
    padding-top: 44px;
    transform: scale(1.04);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.22),
      0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .go-card--best:hover {
    transform: scale(1.04) translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 28px 72px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.28),
      0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
  }

  .go-best-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--go-gold), #e8c96a);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 18px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.4);
  }
  .go-best-text-mobile {
    display: none;
  }
  .go-best-text-desktop {
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .go-size-badge {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--go-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .go-price {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: inherit;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .go-card:not(.go-card--best) .go-price {
    color: var(--go-dark);
  }

  .go-deal-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #f5f0e8;
    color: #9a8060;
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .go-deal-tag--big {
    background: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);
    color: var(--go-gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.3);
  }

  .go-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: #f0ebe3;
    margin: 14px 0;
  }

  .go-card--best .go-divider {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .go-stat-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 4px 0;
    color: #999;
  }

  .go-card--best .go-stat-row {
    color: #aaa;
  }

  .go-stat-row span:last-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #555;
  }

  .go-card--best .go-stat-row span:last-child {
    color: #e0d8c8;
  }

  .go-ppm-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .go-ppm-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #999;
  }

  .go-card--best .go-ppm-label {
    color: #aaa;
  }

  .go-ppm-value {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #555;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }

  .go-ppm-value--best {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--go-gold);
  }

  .go-saving {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--go-gold);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    background: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .go-btn {
    width: 100%;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 15px 20px;
    background: var(--go-dark);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

  .go-btn:hover {
    background: #333;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .go-btn--best {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--go-gold), #ddb93e);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.35);
  }

  .go-btn--best:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b8963e, #c9a84c);
  }

  .go-btn .go-btn-mobile-text {
    display: none;
  }

  .go-modal {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(10, 8, 5, 0.72);
    z-index: 9999;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .go-modal.active {
    display: flex;
  }

  .go-modal-box {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 36px;
    max-width: 540px;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 88vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .go-modal-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 18px;
    right: 18px;
    background: #f5f0e8;
    border: none;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: #888;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .go-modal-close:hover {
    background: #e8e0d5;
  }

  .go-modal-box h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .go-modal-sub {
    color: #999;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .go-progress-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .go-progress-label {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #aaa;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .go-progress-label strong {
    color: var(--go-dark);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .go-progress-bar-bg {
    height: 6px;
    background: #f0ebe3;
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .go-progress-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--go-gold), #ddb93e);
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
    width: 0%;
  }

  .go-scent-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .go-scent-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    border: 2px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    background: none;
  }

  .go-scent-item.has-qty {
    border-color: var(--go-gold);
    background: #fdf9f0;
  }

  .go-scent-item--unavailable {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .go-scent-image {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 2px solid #f0ebe3;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .go-scent-item.has-qty .go-scent-image {
    border-color: var(--go-gold);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.2);
  }

  .go-scent-info {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .go-scent-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .go-scent-variant {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #bbb;
  }

  .go-stepper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1.5px solid #e0d8c8;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .go-stepper-btn {
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    border: none;
    background: #f5f0e8;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    user-select: none;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .go-stepper-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background: var(--go-gold);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .go-stepper-btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.35;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .go-stepper-val {
    width: 34px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--go-dark);
    background: #fff;
    border-left: 1.5px solid #e0d8c8;
    border-right: 1.5px solid #e0d8c8;
    height: 34px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .go-modal-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-top: 20px;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .go-sel-count {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #aaa;
  }

  .go-confirm-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--go-gold), #ddb93e);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    font-size: 15px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.3);
  }

  .go-confirm-btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.35;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .go-confirm-btn:not(:disabled):hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .go-atc-error {
    color: #d32f2f;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08);
    border-radius: 6px;
    border-left: 3px solid #d32f2f;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .great-offer-section {
      padding-inline: 20px;
    }
    .great-offer-section .go-cards {
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .go-card {
      border-radius: 13px;
      padding: 8px 8px 12px;
    }
    .go-card--best {
      /* transform: none; */
    }
    .go-card--best:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
    }

    .go-size-badge {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .go-price {
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .go-deal-tag {
      font-size: 8px;
      padding: 3px 5px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .go-divider {
      margin: 7px 0;
    }
    .go-stat-row {
      font-size: 8px;
      padding: 4px 0;
    }
    .go-stat-row span {
      display: inline-block;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .go-ppm-row {
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .go-ppm-label {
      font-size: 11px;
    }
    .go-ppm-value {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .go-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px 6px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .go-btn .go-btn-mobile-text {
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .go-btn .go-btn-text {
      display: none;
    }
    .go-best-label {
      top: -15px;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      padding: 3px 6px;
    }
    .go-best-text-desktop {
      display: none;
    }
    .go-best-text-mobile {
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .go-saving {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: .3px;
      padding: 6px 6px;
      margin-bottom: 0px;
    }
    .go-modal-box {
      padding: 30px 25px 35px;
    }
    .go-scent-item {
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 12px;
    }
    .go-scent-name {font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4;}
    .go-stepper-btn {
      width: 26px;
      height: 30px;
